ook shows what happened in the glitches between mass communication and interaction, and how Swedish postwar industry worked to disrupt established understandings of communication.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aBusiness communicationxSocial aspectsxHistoryy20th centuryzSweden. 0aBusiness communicationxTechnological innovationsxHistoryy20th centuryzSweden. 0aElectronic office machinesxSocial aspectsxHistoryy20th centuryzSweden. 0aMass mediaxSocial aspectsxHistoryy20th centuryzSweden. 0aMass mediaxTechnological innovationsxHistoryy20th centuryzSweden. 4aCultural Studies. 4aFilm, Media, and Communication. 4aHistory. 4aMedia Studies. 7aART / Film & Video.2bisacsh  ainteraction, objects, cold war, media, social engineering.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311074322708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2021z9783110753790oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2021 Englishz978311075403208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048535835423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048535835/original  a978-3-11-074322-7  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075403-2  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGr